zapping: zapping (tv viewer)
zapping:
zapping: Zapping is a TV viewer for the Gnome desktop. With Zapping and a TV
zapping: card you can watch TV, take screenshots, and record video and audio.
zapping: Zapping has a deinterlacer and a Teletext viewer  built in and
zapping: supports Closed Caption and Teletext subtitles.
